text: thumb Tracey Claire Fisher, better known as Tracey Gold (born May 16, 1969) is an American actress. She is best known for playing Carol Seaver in the sitcom Growing Pains from 1985 until 1992. She also acted in other television programs. Tracey Gold was born in New York City. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:Actors from New York City Category:1969 births Category:Living people
